This is another extension which shows country flag for the site in current
tab. It also shows city, region and country name in the flag icon hint.
Moreover, there are some additional data and links in the popup, refer to
screenshot.

Extension loads geo data from http://ipinfodb.com/. All data is cached
locally, so minimal number of additional requests is made.
Cached data is invalidated after storing for 30 days.

Extension was tested on WinXP SP3, Win7 (incl. x64), Linux and Mac OS X.